{
  "stem": "893.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And towards-- towards the end of December, we had another incident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the village drunkard, sort of, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who was-- who got friendly with one of the-- with a Russian partisan who parachuted into the forest and got lost from his unit-- befriended him.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, sort of, the drunkard must have heard from the other villagers where we bought our provisions and our blankets and everything else, that we had money.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He must have told them that there is a way of getting some money from some rich people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came to our hiding place, that drunkard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was armed with a hack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the partisan had a handgun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First he was nice to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We spoke Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, the Russian couldn't tell that-- you know, what we are.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the drunkard for sure couldn't tell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they wanted money from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We told them, we have no money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We come from families of-- of-- modest [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people, modest-- we didn't have no money on us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were on-- on a state stipend, studying in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For him, we told us we are students, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just don't have no money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So since my brother looks much like myself, so he decided, the Russian, that he'll threaten one of us--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] --with harm, and maybe we'll give him the money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he told my-- he told us-- he told my brother-- he'll take me, and if he'll have to, he'll kill me if I don't give the money.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have-- you know, the only thing-- the only money we had was American currency.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a $100 bill, and not too much Slovakian currency.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we needed the money to survive, so we stuck to our story.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
